Package org.botblock.javabotblockapi

Enum Site

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Site>
      • org.botblock.javabotblockapi.Site
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Site>
    public enum Site
extends Enum<Site>
    Enum class containing all sites currently supported by BotBlock.org.

    The fields can be used in:

    • GetBotAction
    • GetListAction or
    • BotBlockAPI.Builder
    Since:
    2.1.0
